<p><a name="Table_of_MTUs_of_common_media" id="Table_of_MTUs_of_common_media"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Maximum_transmission_unit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Table of MTUs of common media">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Table of MTUs of common media</span></h2>
<p>Note: the MTUs in this section are given as the maximum size of IP packet that can be transmitted without fragmentation including IP headers but excluding headers from lower levels in the protocol stack.</p>
<table class="wikitable">
<tr>
