<td>At least 576</td>
<td>Practical path MTUs are generally higher. Systems may use <a href="/wiki/Path_MTU_discovery" title="Path MTU discovery">path MTU discovery</a> (<a href="http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1191" class="external" title="http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1191">RFC 1191</a>) to find the actual path MTU.</td>
