<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREF.22The_Cable_Guy.222005">"The Cable Guy" (November 2005). <a href="http://technet.microsoft.com/en-gb/library/bb878127.aspx" class="external text" title="http://technet.microsoft.com/en-gb/library/bb878127.aspx" rel="nofollow">"Performance Enhancements in the Next Generation TCP/IP Stack"</a>. Microsoft Corporation<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://technet.microsoft.com/en-gb/library/bb878127.aspx" class="external free" title="http://technet.microsoft.com/en-gb/library/bb878127.aspx" rel="nofollow">http://technet.microsoft.com/en-gb/library/bb878127.aspx</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Performance+Enhancements+in+the+Next+Generation+TCP%2FIP+Stack&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=%22The+Cable+Guy%22&amp;rft.au=%22The+Cable+Guy%22&amp;rft.date=November+2005&amp;rft.pub=Microsoft+Corporation&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnet.microsoft.com%2Fen-gb%2Flibrary%2Fbb878127.aspx&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Maximum_transmission_unit"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
